    "description": "<ul>  <li><b>100% WATERPROOF:</b> Our dry bags made of 500D PVC material and designed with roll-top closure.It has good waterproof, dustproof and scratch-resistant performance. Protects your items from water, sand, dust and dirt.</li>  <li><b>ANTI LEAK AND ANTI TEAR:</b> The dry bag features fully welded seams by high-frequency tech, provides a stronger and more durably waterproof construction. Abrasion resistant for long lasting. It is a great choice as gift to outdoorsy women and men.</li>  <li><b>MULTIPLE CHOICES:</b> The dry bag backpack comes with 5 sizes (5L/10L/20L/30/40L). 5L, 10L and 20L dry bags include single detachable strap, can be cross-body or shoulder-carried; 30L and 40L dry bags include double detachable straps, can use as a backpack.</li>  <li><b>MULTIPLE PURPOSE:</b> Multi-size dry bags waterproof backpack provice better storage space. It can hold your phones, camera, wallet, tool, sunblock, clothes, towels and other duffel. Perfect for outdoor survival, hiking, camping, climbing, biking , water sports like kayaking, canoeing, fishing, rafting, boating, swimming, surfing.</li>  <li><b>EASY TO USE:</b> Just put your gear in bag, grab top woven tape and roll down tightly 3 to 5 times and then plug buckle to complete seal, whole process is very easy and quick. In order to help your bag float on the water better, be sure to leave some extra room for the air.</li> </ul>",
